title: Arbor Snowboards :: Product Profiles - Swoon
description:
A rocker board designed for women who take on big mountains; the Swoon is a freeriding wonder that was designed to provide easy performance, reliability, control, and confidence when riding the full range of real mountain conditions.

To learn more about the Swoon visit: http://arborcollective.com/snowboards
